<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    #set($src="http://f.51fanbei.com/h5/app/activity/08")
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>赠送页面</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/dist/activity/08/ggpresents.css?version=$version">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="presents">
        <div class="presents-top">
            <div class="box" id="scroll_div">
                <div class="personAmount" id="scroll_begin"><p>已有<span class="light">11</span>人点亮所有场景</p><p>已有<span class="light">222</span>人点亮所有场景</p></div>
                <div class="personAmount" id="scroll_end"></div>     
                <!--<div class="personAmount"><p>已有<span class="light"></span>22222222222</p></div>!-->
            </div>
            <div class="header">
                <div class="logo"><img src="$src/gg01.png"></div>
                <p class="joinAmount"><span class="join"></span>人参与</p>
            </div>
            <div class="money">
                <p><i class="friend"></i>在51返呗点亮场景</p>
                <p><span class="combo"></span>送给你</p>
            </div>
            <div class="banner">
                <img src="" alt="" class="banner-img">
            </div>
            <div class="send">
                <div class="presentCard ask">我要赠送卡片</div>
                <div class="demandCard ask">我要索要卡片</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="presents-bottom clearFix">
            <div class="presents-bottom-right">
                <div class="line">
                    <span class="number-one">1</span>
                    <span class="number-two">2</span>
                    <span class="number-three">3</span>
                </div>
                
            </div>
            <div class="presents-bottom-left">
                <p class="word-one">
                    <span>完成1笔消费订单且满足消费规<br/>则时,即可获得1张场景专属卡片<br/>更有高额返利</span>
                </p>
                <p class="word-two">
                    <span>向好友索要、与好友互换,即可<br/>获取不同种类的专属卡片;分享<br/>后,好友消费后更有同等返利给<br/>到你</span>
                </p>
                <p class="word-three">
                    <span>集齐全部专属卡片,即可兑换<br/>88.88元现金红包</span>
                </p>
                <div class="rules"><a href="#">活动规则详情</a></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--活动规则弹框!-->
        
        <div class="mask">
            <div class="alertRule">
                <p class="ruleTitle"><span class="dian"></span><span class="word">活动规则</span><span class="dian"></span></p>
                <p class="ruleCont"></p>
                <p class="close">X</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/dist/activity/08/ggpresents.js?version=$version"></script>
</html>
